cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language generation (nlg) and semantic representation of story structures, which are topics that fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves training translation rules and measuring string similarity metrics, which are techniques that fall under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SD).
